// Basic psql commands

//I've created "database_labs" database through pgAdmin interface, and tried to connect to it through psql with different commands
PS C:\Users\sulta> psql --version
psql (PostgreSQL) 17.6
PS C:\Users\sulta> psql -h localhost -p 5432 -U postgres -d database_labs
Password for user postgres:

